Consumption
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
We assume a single representative consumer that supplies 
\begin_inset Formula $L$
\end_inset

 units of labor inelastically and consumes the good with the utility function
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
U(x)=x,
\]

\end_inset

where 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 is the good.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
